      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery has some staining and wear from regular use. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in optimal shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point.",
